
REQUIREMENTS:
  - QT 4 (required)
  - ffmpeg (required)
  - pulseaudio (required)
  - pulsaudio-utils (required)
  - alsa (required)
  - alsa-utils (required)
  - lame (required)
  - libmp3lame0 (required)
  - v4l-utils
  - mkvtoolnix

Compile:
  - extract vokoscren-<version>.tar
  - change in the vokoscreen-<version> directory
  - make

openSUSE:
Install Schemata: QT 4-Development
  
Hint:
To check that all external programs are installed,
please vokoscreen on the console to run and control
the output section ---Begin Search external tools--- 
